cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for material recognition using a new light-field dataset. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects, as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
